title: A girl in an orange shirt plays trombone at a basketball game.
shortDescription: The player is wearing an orange shirt and has her eyes closed as she plays the trumpet.
longDescription: In the center of the image, a young woman in an orange shirt is the main focus. She's holding a brass instrument, specifically a silver trombone, to her lips and appears to be blowing into it. The background is dark, but there are hints of other people and musical instruments visible. The player seems focused on her performance, oblivious to the bustling atmosphere around her.
